{"title":"巴拿马，愤怒的河！","authors":["袁鹰"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，愤怒的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你经历多少年代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听见过多少悲歌？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六七万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开河工人的白骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"换来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄灿灿的金元，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚北流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百多万"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民的血泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉不尽重重灾难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地惨天愁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马运河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一把钢刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺进了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马的心口；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条铁索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒住了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马的咽喉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国舰队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横冲直撞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"践踏着你的胸脯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国商船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张开血口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞噬着你的财富。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“绿色的强盗”〔注〕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霸占了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵延的香蕉林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少印第安工人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冤仇无处诉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的咖啡可可，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴上了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国商标；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街老板的赌注。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的珊瑚玳瑁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装饰了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纽约贵妇人的衣橱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多么富饶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又多么褴褛；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你多么甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又多么苦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自己的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马国旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能随风飘展；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在自己的河岸上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能自由行走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是强盗的法律，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的紧箍咒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在痛苦里挣扎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不能忍受！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运河的水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在沸腾！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两洋的浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在奔流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刽子手的屠刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吓不倒义旗高举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡不住滚滚洪流！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱国者的鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震响了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五湖四海的风雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激起了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊天动地的怒吼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愤怒的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准凶恶的敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举钢铁的拳头！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在苦难的大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点起熊熊的烈火！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗击美国强盗的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震撼旧世界的河！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月十二日夜北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕美国的垄断资本“联合果品公司”，操纵着巴拿马和许多拉丁美洲国家的经济命脉。拉丁美洲人咒骂它为“绿色的强盗”。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}